OL,3,CAirbnb bans indoor security cameras in
OL,4,Cpush to improve privacy
OL,6,FHoliday rental company Airbnb has
OL,7,Fbanned the use of indoor security
OL,8,Fcameras in properties listed on its
OL,9,Fsite as it tries to improve privacy
OL,10,Ffor users.
OL,12,FThe announcement comes after a rise in
OL,13,Fsocial media videos showing people how
OL,14,Fto check rental accommodation for
OL,15,Fhidden cameras.
