OL,3,CAirbnb bans indoor security cameras in
OL,4,Cpush to improve privacy
OL,6,FBefore the new rules were
OL,7,Fimplemented,allowed the use of indoor
OL,8,Fsecurity cameras in common areas, such
OL,9,Fas hallways and living rooms, as long
OL,10,Fas they were disclosed on the listing
OL,11,Fpage before booking.
OL,13,FThe cameras also had to be in plain
OL,14,Fsight and were not allowed to be
OL,15,Flocated in spaces such as sleeping
OL,16,Fareas and bathrooms.
OL,18,FThe update clarifies that any indoor
OL,19,Fsecurity camera are now banned in a
OL,20,Flisting, regardless of location,
OL,21,Fpurpose or prior disclosure.
