OL,3,CAirbnb bans indoor security cameras in
OL,4,Cpush to improve privacy
OL,6,FJuniper Downs, head of community
OL,7,Fpolicy and partnerships at Airbnb,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Our goal was to create new,
OL,9,Fclear rules that provide our community
OL,10,Fwith greater clarity about what to
OL,11,Fexpect on Airbnb.
OL,13,F"These changes were made in
OL,14,Fconsultation with our guests, Hosts
OL,15,Fand privacy experts, and we'll
OL,16,Fcontinue to seek feedback to help
OL,17,Fensure our policies work for our
OL,18,Fglobal community."
