OL,6,FShe added that the had been drafted
OL,7,Falongside guests, hosts and privacy
OL,8,Fexperts.
OL,10,FThe firm emphasised that the majority
OL,11,Fof Airbnb listings do not report
OL,12,Fhaving a security camera - so the
OL,13,Fannouncement should only affect a
OL,14,Fsmall number of hosts.
OL,16,FHosts who currently make use of an
OL,17,Findoor security camera can continue to
OL,18,Fdo so until April 30.
