OL,3,CAirbnb bans indoor security cameras in
OL,4,Cpush to improve privacy
OL,6,FAfter this date, any host who still
OL,7,Fhas a camera within their property
OL,8,Fcould face their listing and account
OL,9,Fstruck off the platform.
OL,11,FOutdoor cameras, such as doorbell
OL,12,Fcameras, will continue to be allowed
OL,13,Fby Airbnb. But, hosts will have to
OL,14,Fdisclose their location to guests
OL,15,Fbefore they book.
OL,17,FThe use of indoor cameras has long
OL,18,Fbeen a point of contention for those
OL,19,Fmaking use of the platform, arguing
OL,20,Fthat they are an invasion of privacy.
